dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents State Assembly Districts for Wisconsin in 2022. [Legislative districts were adopted by the Wisconsin Supreme Court via Johnson v. Wisconsin Elections Commission, Case No. 2021AP1450-OA on April 15, 2022. Data was appended to U.S. Census TIGER 2020 Block geography with 2020 US Census PL 94-171 Demographic Data and dissolved by district.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For additional information and most current data, please visit https://gis-ltsb.hub.arcgis.com/.
